set_domain

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_domain -  This sets the domain the NPC is restricted to.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_domain(string domain)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^domain%^RESET%^ - the first 6 letters of the domain-path, ie "/d/am/"
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/locksmith.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This sets the domain the NPC is restricted to.
.EP

